   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00129"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb415">Aussee</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>30/7 900</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute> heute wurde folgender Plan fe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tellt.</p><p><date>12. August</date>
             (So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag) <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs></p><p><date>13.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs>.</p><p><date>14.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell
                  am See</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><add place="below">(Bahn.)</add></p><p>Ausflug auf den <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90148">Moserboden</rs>.</p><p><date>15.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb90148">Moserboden</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell am See</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb867">Innsbruck</rs> (Bahn.)</p><p>16. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb867">Innsbruck</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90366">Bludenz</rs> (Bahn) – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb38711">Schruns</rs> (Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t)</p><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00130-0"/><date>17.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>18.</date> Aufenthalt in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb38711">Schruns</rs>. (event. zu verlängern)</p><p><date>19.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Beginn den Fußtour, die etwa
                  <date>22.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><unclear>recht</unclear>, von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs>
               entweder nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49343">Bormio</rs>, dann <rs type="place" ref="#pmb91918">Trafoi</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb91855">Sulden</rs>, oder <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49343">Bormio</rs> – nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40306">Italien</rs> (<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142872">Lago d’Iseo</rs></hi>) oder von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs> in die <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs>. Ich hoffe, da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Sie minde<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens vom
                  <date>12. </date>bis <date>19.</date> mitthun. <pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00130-1"/>Aber überlegen Sie, ob Sie <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich nicht
               doch zu der Fußpartie ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chließen. Schreiben Sie mir bitte nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">I<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chl</rs>, <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb414">Rudolfshöhe</rs></hi>, wohin ich morgen ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>egle.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur.</signed></closer><postscript><p>Könnten Sie nicht auch nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">I<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chl</rs> kommen?</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
